data.description: Fantastic Updated Home providing 2,154sf of Living Space, 3 Bedrooms, Huge Bonus(or 4th Room), & 2.5 Bathrooms. Beautiful Kitchen with Quartz Counters, Stainless Appliances + Gas Range. Formal Dining Room adjacent to Kitchen. Formal Living Room. Family Room with Fireplace. Mounted TV's Stay! Primary Suite features Walk-in Closet, Workout/Reading Area, Additional Double Closet, and Full Bathroom. Fenced Backyard with Huge Deck partially Covered, Perfect for Entertaining. Gas, A/C, plus New Hot Water Heater. Quiet Neighborhood on a No Thru Street!
